            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center md:space-x-8">
                <div class="md:w-1/3 mb-6 md:mb-0">
                    <img src="https://placehold.co/300x300/1e3a8a/d1d5db?text=Karriem+Perry" alt="Karriem A.J. Perry" class="rounded-full shadow-lg border-4 border-orange-500 mx-auto w-48 h-48 object-cover">
                </div>
                <div class="md:w-2/3 text-lg leading-relaxed">
                    <p class="mb-4">Hi there! I'm a theoretical quantum machine learning researcher, data scientist, and adjunct professor. With a background in psychology, data analytics, AI, and quantum computing, my work spans the frontiers of AI, complex systems, possibility theory, and statistical-relational learning. He holds a BA in Psychology from Ottawa University (KS), an MS in Data Analytics from Southern New Hampshire University (NH), a Ph.D. in AI, and I'm currently pursuing a second Ph.D. in Quantum Computing at Capitol Technology University (MD). This cross-disciplinary approach has led me to incorporate complex systems science into my current research.</p>
                    <p>As a former Green Beret and Army Ranger, when I'm not researching, Karriem is either biking, hiking, on my MTB, or building his tech startups: JIANT Systems, LLC and UltraMassive Advanced Scientific Research Corporation.</p>
